cu.explanation_en: Setting the tracking area code to a reserved value (0x0000) will cause network registration and mobility issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting the tracking area code to a reserved value (0x0000) will cause network registration and mobility issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將追蹤區域代碼設定為保留值 (0x0000) 將導致網路註冊和移動性問題。
